### Architecture Lakehouse (Médaillon)

```
SAP_Bronze (schema-enabled)              Domain_Lakehouse (schema-enabled)
  dbo.bronze_zcds_*  ◄──── schema shortcut ────  bronze.*
                                                   silver.* (vues calculées)
                                                   gold.*   (agrégats métier)
```

### Convention Hashkeys

- PK : `_pk_hkey_{fields}` (SHA256 sur les champs clés)
- FK : `_fk_hkey_{business_keys}`
- Jointures : `fact._fk_hkey_{bk} = dim._pk_hkey_{bk}`
